        "message": "Patch Set 9: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/oom-master-verify-helm/987/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/oom-master-verify-helm/987",
